NOTICE OF INTENTION TO INTRODUCE LOCAL LEGISLATION
Notice is given that there will be introduced at the 2025 regular session of the General Assembly
of Georgia a bill to amend an Act creating a State Court of Henry County, approved March 27, 1998
(Ga. L. 1998, p. 3954), as amended; and for other purposes.
3:5, 2025
AFFIDAVIT
GEORGIA, FULTON COUNTY
